# Refactoring Report â€” To-Do List App

## Original Issues:
- Poor variable naming
- Inline `onclick` usage
- Lack of structure and reusability
- No UX optimizations

## Refactoring Done:
- Separated logic into reusable functions
- Used descriptive variable names
- Added Enter key support for better UX
- Applied CSS styling for improved UI
- Used event listeners instead of inline handlers

## Performance Impact:
- DOM updates optimized through central function
- Reduced unnecessary code repetition
- Better maintainability and scalability
